---- About ----

University task. See [1].

[1] (RU) http://courses.graphicon.ru/main/cg/2012/assignment04

---- Dependencies ----

* opengl 3.3;
* glew;
* glfw.

---- Navigation, keys, buttons ----

Slide: WASD, Page Up/Page Down, move mouse with pressed left or right shift.

Rotate: arrows, Q, E, move mouse.

Make wave: left mouse button.

On/off vsync: F8.

On/off pause: Pause key.

Exit: Esc.
